            <div id="primary-content">
              <a name="37347"></a><h1>Personnel Services</h1>





<p>This site provides information about the University's personnel policies and procedures. There is a search facility at the top of the screen and an <a href="/personnel/a-z/">A-Z</a> to help you find what you are looking for.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The site is updated regularly: please click Ctrl+F5 (refresh) whenever you open a page, and check that any old print-outs are still current against the guidance and documentation published here. We welcome your <a href="mailto:personnel.services@admin.ox.ac.uk">feedback</a>.&nbsp;</p>
